pageContext.claim: “I took the toughest-ever action to stand up to China's pillaging plundering, ransacking, and rampant theft of North Carolina jobs and U.S. jobs. Joe Biden's agenda is made in China. My agenda is made in the U.S.A.”
pageContext.analysis: This is over-the-top rhetoric. Biden’s platform is shaped by the American Democratic Party, not China or any other foreign power.
